## 7. Git Automation & Workflow (Mandatory)

### 7.1. Commit Message Convention
- Format: \`docs: [Blog Title] 포스팅 작성\`
- Logic: Extract the \`title\` value from the Front Matter (YAML) of the created file.

### 7.2. Execution Steps
Once the markdown file is saved, proceed with these commands immediately:
1. \`git add [Exact File Path]\`
2. \`git commit -m "docs: [Extracted Title] 포스팅 작성"\`
3. \`git push origin main\`

### 7.3. Error Handling
- If the push fails due to a conflict, alert the user and do not force push.

